snippet.title: Bishoujo Senshi Sailor Moon S [美少女 戦士 セーラー ムーン S] Game Sample - Game Gear
snippet.description:
Original Air Date: December 14th, 2008

One of the common Japanese Game Gear games, it's a simple action game. You can play as either Sailor Moon or Mini Moon, as well as mini-games.
